{"tid":1501011,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[很重要] 燈柱拆左就要影部件","createTime":"2019-08-24T08:20:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T09:12:25.000Z","uid":157454,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6a980be3165dba8edbb1c6895d869904c354a5ca","tid":1501011,"uid":157454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:20:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">搵人去幫手影清楚啲組件？？？？</span></em></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n影埋佢哋個藍牙同埋rfid偵測裝置<br />\n<br />\n如果有啲拆左出嚟嘅嘢<br />\n可以逐樣逐樣影清楚<br />\n尤其是<span style=\"color: red;\">晶片名稱</span>或者<span style=\"color: red;\">任何編碼</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">鏡頭型號</span><br />\n<br />\n呢啲技術資料可以畀專家做分析<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><em>拎上民間記者會</em></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n取得呢個燈柱嘅詳細資料<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有助取得更多關於大灣區未被公佈嘅部署資料</span></span>"},{"pid":"7599c180da6478f78c50e4cd7404d8eec38ef34c","tid":1501011,"uid":157454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:25:53.000Z","msg":"自推十式。一"},{"pid":"25e75f299807ed1ba1d7d229f5507e67a0980e0c","tid":1501011,"uid":157454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:26:05.000Z","msg":"自推十式。二"},{"pid":"a500983b49e8fb3b0f2ba6d0cfb3e30e75f8b93f","tid":1501011,"uid":279779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:26:14.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"a115eabdba4c2b73ff15d0385b4bff3822c2ad22","tid":1501011,"uid":157454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:26:51.000Z","msg":"自推十式。三"},{"pid":"cc331ee0ba4c7b081799940166ef2243ebadae59","tid":1501011,"uid":157454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:28:09.000Z","msg":"自推十式。四"},{"pid":"75a794f0f13ede2e8c388f89ada4964b791fc850","tid":1501011,"uid":157454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24